description:
Not all the ancestors of Jesus had squeaky clean resumes. If you look at His family tree there are some downright shady characters listed. Jesus came to save the human race, warts and all. That goes for us too. And that is why we can be called children of God, part of the heavenly family. Watch this video to find out about the human roots of Jesus, His family tree.
